20:53.502 --> 20:54.674
I'll take two!

20:54.837 --> 20:56.009
Kimberley will take two.

20:56.797 --> 20:58.515
You get Lacan's point.

20:59.175 --> 21:02.270
Fantasies have
to be unrealistic.

21:02.344 --> 21:05.598
Because the moment, the second
that you get what you seek,

21:05.681 --> 21:08.400
you don't,
you can't want it anymore.

21:08.476 --> 21:10.945
In order to continue to exist,

21:11.020 --> 21:15.070
